      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BoardGame
      BoardGame is a specifaction of Game class because it represents a particular type of game (a role-playing game or party game).
      class  Book
      Book inherits from Document class and represents a book identified by an ISBN.
      class  CD
      CD inherits from Disc class and represents a compact disc.
      class  Comic
      Comic is a specifaction of Book class because it represents a particular type of book (a strip cartoon).
      class  Disc
      Disc is the abstract base class for documents subclasses related with disc supports like DVD, CD, etc...
      class  DVD
      DVD inherits from Disc class and represents a Digital Versatile Disc.
      class  Game
      Game is the abstract base class for document subclasses related with playing universe like video games, board games, etc...
      class  Other
      Other class is a specification of the Document class used to represent documents that doesn't matches with an existing subclass.
      class  Plan
      Plan class is a specification of the Document class that represents documents corresponding to a map.
      class  Review
      Review class is a specification of the Document class used to represent documents corresponding to a report or a revision.
      class  SheetMusic
      SheetMusic class is a specification of the Document class that represents documents corresponding to a tablature / a music score.
      class  VideoGame
      VideoGame inherits from Game class and represents an electronic game.
      class  VinylDisc
      VinylDisc is a specifaction of Disc class because it represents a particular type of disc (a vinyl record).
